Cube.Name: UNITS_CUBE
Cube.ConsistentSolve: SOLVE ( SUM OVER "TIME", SUM OVER CHANNEL, SUM OVER CUSTOMER, SUM OVER PRODUCT )

AWCubeOrganization.DefaultBuild: BUILD SPEC Load_and_Aggregate ( LOAD NO SYNCH, SOLVE, ANALYZE )

BuildSpecifications.Value: BUILD SPEC Load_and_Aggregate ( LOAD NO SYNCH, SOLVE, ANALYZE )

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_3_PER_MOVAVG
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: AVG(UNITS_CUBE.SALES) OVER HIERARCHY ("TIME".CALENDAR BETWEEN 2 PRECEDING AND CURRENT MEMBER WITHIN LEVEL)

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_CHG_PP
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: LAG_VARIANCE(UNITS_CUBE.SALES, 1) OVER HIERARCHY ("TIME".CALENDAR)

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_CHG_PY
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: LAG_VARIANCE(UNITS_CUBE.SALES, 1) OVER HIERARCHY ("TIME".CALENDAR BY ANCESTOR AT LEVEL "TIME".CALENDAR.CALENDAR_YEAR POSITION FROM BEGINNING)

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_PCT_CHG_PP
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: LAG_VARIANCE_PERCENT(UNITS_CUBE.SALES, 1) OVER HIERARCHY ("TIME".CALENDAR) * 100

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_PCT_CHG_PY

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_PROD_PRNT_SHARE

DerivedMeasure.Name: SALES_PROD_TOT_SHARE

DerivedMeasure.Name: PROFIT
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: UNITS_CUBE.SALES - UNITS_CUBE.COST

DerivedMeasure.Name: HOW_IS_MARGIN
DerivedMeasure.MeasureExpression: CASE WHEN UNITS_CUBE.PROFIT / UNITS_CUBE.SALES > 0.2 THEN 'GROOVY' WHEN UNITS_CUBE.PROFIT / UNITS_CUBE.SALES < 0.1 THEN 'YIPES' ELSE 'WHATEVER' END
